    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly in such solid shape. It\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more adventures with a new owner. It runs great, looks sharp, and is perfect if you're looking for something reliable and ready to go right now. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
