    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six and a row-your-own 6-speed manual. This unit boasts a broad power band thanks to its individual throttle bodies and a recently serviced Double VANOS system. The chassis remains taut with documented subframe reinforcement and a limited-slip differential that ensures surgical corner exits. While showing minor cosmetic signs of use, its mechanical performance is sharp, bolstered by a refreshed cooling system and precise suspension geometry. A high-revving, analog legend ready for the open road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
